## Table documents
- id, folder_id (FK), document_type (FK document_types), file_path (S3)
- status ENUM : 'pending_analysis' | 'valid' | 'rejected' | 'expired'
- ai_score, ai_warnings (JSON), extracted_data (JSON chiffré)
